{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "TubeConv API",
    "description": "ðŸŽµ **YouTube to MP3 Converter API**\n\nConvert YouTube videos to high-quality MP3 files with ease. This API provides a simple and powerful interface for downloading and converting YouTube content.\n\n## Features\n- ðŸŽ¯ **High-Quality Audio**: Support for 128kbps to 320kbps bitrates\n- ðŸš€ **Fast Processing**: Optimized conversion pipeline\n- ðŸ”’ **Secure**: Rate limiting and input validation\n- ðŸ“± **Mobile-Friendly**: Responsive design\n- ðŸ§¹ **Auto-Cleanup**: Temporary files are automatically removed\n\n## Rate Limits\n- **General**: 100 requests per 15 minutes\n- **Conversions**: 5 requests per 15 minutes\n- **Previews**: 20 requests per 5 minutes\n\n## Error Codes\n- `MISSING_URL`: URL parameter is required\n- `INVALID_URL`: Invalid YouTube URL format\n- `INVALID_QUALITY`: Invalid audio quality specified\n- `TITLE_TOO_LONG`: Title exceeds 100 characters\n- `ARTIST_TOO_LONG`: Artist name exceeds 100 characters\n- `PREVIEW_ERROR`: Failed to fetch video information\n- `CONVERSION_ERROR`: Failed to convert video\n\n## Usage Examples\n\n### Preview a Video\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \\\n  http://localhost:3000/api/preview \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ\"}'\n```\n\n### Convert a Video\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \\\n  http://localhost:3000/api/convert \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ\",\n    \"audioQuality\": \"320\",\n    \"metadata\": {\n      \"title\": \"Rick Astley - Never Gonna Give You Up\",\n      \"artist\": \"Rick Astley\"\n    }\n  }'\n```",
    "version": "1.0.0",
